  <h1>HR & Recruitment Jobs</h1>

  <p>Human Resources (HR) jobs focus on hiring, managing employees, and building a strong company culture. These roles are ideal for people who enjoy working with others.</p>

  <h2>Common Roles</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>HR Executive</li>
    <li>Recruiter</li>
    <li>Talent Acquisition Specialist</li>
    <li>HR Coordinator</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Skills Required</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Communication skills</li>
    <li>People management</li>
    <li>Organization</li>
    <li>Decision-making ability</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Why Choose HR?</h2>
  <p>HR offers long-term career growth and opportunities to move into leadership roles.</p>

  <h2>Where to Apply</h2>
  <p>Corporate companies, recruitment agencies, and startups regularly hire HR professionals.</p>

